  <a class="pg-btn" href="/semaglutide">SEMAGLUTIDE</a>
  <h4 class="pg-h">Transformative Body Treatments &amp; Wellness</h4>
  <p class="pg-text">At Menon MediSpa, we blend clinical expertise with luxury to deliver transformative body treatments, IV vitamin therapy, laser hair removal, and medically supervised weight management.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Our medical-grade services address specific body concerns using proven technologies and pharmaceutical-grade products. Led by expert medical professionals, each treatment is tailored to your unique needs and goals.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">From enhancing wellness with IV therapy to removing unwanted hair with advanced laser technology, our cutting-edge treatments provide visible, long-lasting results. Experience the difference of clinically-effective treatments in our serene Millburn, NJ medical spa.</p>
</section>

<section class="pg-section" data-section="What Our Clients Say">
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/30cfb9e87c60.png" alt="Untitled-4.png" width="1440" height="626" loading="lazy" />
  <h3 class="pg-h">What Our Clients Say</h3>
  <blockquote class="pg-quote">Jennifer is amazing. Her aura and energy makes you feel welcomed and comfortable. Love our sessions! And my girl Rose Marie, the receptionist, is just lovely! I always leave with great joy after seeing them.</blockquote>
